column5: Played well on Helios, but had a tendency to run ahead of team and overextend, leaving the backline vulnerable.
Very solid Artemis gameplay, yet often split from team to be a one-man army. Wasn't punished by enemy team for it, but that's not a guarantee forever.
Kept trying to one-trick with Athena to mediocre results. Hades gameplay was average. Several instances of toxic all-chat behavior.
Heavily needs to work on communicating during team fights, but otherwise good.
Had some trouble playing Ra, but performed quite well using Persephone. Great team fight coordination.
